<font color="WHITE">Calendar - May 1997</font></td></tr></tbody></table>
<h1><center>Mt. St. Helens Field Trip</center></h1>
<h2><center>August 24 - 30, 1997</center></h2>
<p>

Last month, at our Fourth Friday Free Film, we showed

a video that described the marvelous geological formations that

were made as a result of the 1980 eruption of Mount St. Helens.

Now you have an opportunity to go to Mount St. Helens and see

these wonders for yourself.

</p><p>

The <a data-original-url="http://www.icr.org" data-wayback-date="" href="http://www.icr.org">Institute for Creation Research </a>will

be conducting a 4-day tour of Mount St. Helens with an optional

3-day extension to explore the flood-scoured geology of Eastern

Washington. Prices for the 4-day and 7-day trips are $325 and

$865 per person, respectively. For more information write to ICR,

P.O. Box 2667, El Cajon, CA 92021. Or, if you prefer, call them

at (619) 448-0900.



